# macedonian sky culture name
msgid "Macedonian"
msgstr "马其顿"

# macedonian sky culture introduction section in markdown format
msgid ""
"This sky culture has been created based on the _Sky map of Macedonian people_\n"
"reconstructed from the descriptions of constellations known to elderly\n"
"inhabitants of Macedonian villages."
msgstr "这种天空文化是根据马其顿人民的天空地图创建的，该地图是根据马其顿村庄老年人的星座描述重新构建的。"

# macedonian sky culture description section in markdown format
msgid ""
"Ethnoastronomical research among Macedonian people began in 1982, organized by\n"
"the Planetarium at Youth Cultural Centre. In the past years, around 140\n"
"villages in Republic of Macedonia have been visited and over 1500 inhabitants\n"
"have been interviewed and surveyed. All collected information from the\n"
"population have been published in the book “Sky over Macedonia” (Cenev G,\n"
"2004). An integral part of this book is the Sky map of Macedonian people which\n"
"has been reconstructed based on the descriptions of constellations known to\n"
"elderly inhabitants of Macedonian villages (Cenev G., 2000)."
msgstr ""
"马其顿人民的民族天文学研究始于1982年，由青年文化中心的天文馆组织。在过去的几年中，马其顿共和国约有140个村庄被访问，并采访和调查了1500多名居民。从人口中收集的所有信息均已出版在《马其顿上空的天空》（Cenev"
" G，2004）一书中。本书不可分割的一部分是马其顿人的天空地图，该地图是根据马其顿村庄老年人的星座描述进行重建的（Cenev G.，2000）。"

