" - [#2]: Stellarium Script: Sardinian Constellations Tour. [Link](http://www.stellarium.org/wiki/index.php/Scripts)"
msgstr ""
" - [#1]: 撒丁岛语言中的星星和星座。 [链接](http://www.sarabu.it/193_521_news_2863.php)\n"
" - [#2]: Stellarium脚本：撒丁岛星座之旅。 [链接](http://www.stellarium.org/wiki/index.php/Scripts)"

